            <note>The original incorrect spelling cannot be <foreign>mera</foreign>, as this inscription makes the distinction between medial <foreign>ā</foreign> and <foreign>ra</foreign>. Both <ptr target="bib:VaidyanathaAiyar+SwaminathaAiyar1929_02"/> and <ptr target="bib:Subbarayalu2015_01"/> read a <foreign>piḷḷaiyār cūḻi</foreign> after this final word, but there is no punctuation mark on the stone.</note>
          </app>
