      <div resp="part:emfr" type="translation">
        <p n="1">
      			Prosperity!
      		</p>
        <p n="1-3">
      			5th year of the victorious king Tantippōttaraiyaṉ<note>That is, the Pallava king Dantin, that is, Dantivarman.</note>
      		</p>
        <p n="3-6">
      			<supplied reason="subaudible">This is</supplied> the pond that Kalimūrkka-Iḷavaraiyaṉ, alias Vāḻi Vaṭukaṉ, a servant of the honourable king Pērati, alias Māṟappiṭuviṉār, made; <supplied reason="subaudible">its name is</supplied> the Vāli tank.
      		</p>
        <p n="6-7">
      			The feet of he who protects this pond are on my head.
      		</p>
      </div>
